CBRE is delighted to offer 31 Cabot Drive, Altona North for sale.

This specialised warehouse presents the chance to be in the highly sought after Millers Junction Business Park. 

The unit has been equipped with floor to ceiling sound panels, seven internal and external security cameras, block out blinds, air-conditioned warehouse and office, fully functional kitchen, lockable office, lockable storage room, additional 20sqm* of storage space and entertainment system. 

The property is currently a state-of-the-art photography studio facility with an impressive double wall CYCLORAMA. Great for video productions, TVC, corporate videos, vehicle and commercial photography. 

The studio is located just 15 mins* from Melbourne CBD at Millers Junction, Altona North. There are 4 onsite parks & plenty of free all day parking available at Millers Junction with easy access to local cafes & shops. 

Major retailers are already located at Millers Junction, including Bunnings, Officeworks, Aldi, JB HiFi, Repco, Autobarn, Jaycar and PETstock. The existing appeal of the Centre to a broad cross-section of consumers will help drive high foot traffic to the site. 

The new Retail Centre will add circa 13,000sqm* of lettable area, creating a combined shopping precinct of nearly 35,000sqm and parking for over 1,600 vehicles (set to be complete Q4 2019). 

31 Cabot Drive is positioned:
- 2km* to Geelong Road/Princes Highway
- 5km* to Port of Melbourne
-2.5km* to M80 Western Ring Road
- 9km* to Melbourne CBD
- 16km* to Melbourne Airport
